changeComments(ActionEvent) - Method in class AdminDash.AdminController
This method changes the comments of the specified book by updating the SQL library table and refreshing all TableViews
changeUser(ActionEvent) - Method in class AdminDash.AdminController
this method sets the textfields to the current information of the user being changed so the admin changing the info can determine what they need to change
checkin(ActionEvent) - Method in class AdminDash.AdminController
This method is attached to the check in button in the Library tab's Check in/Check out sub-tab, it runs checks to see if the book is available and will check it in for the user specified by ID if the book is currently out.
checkout(ActionEvent) - Method in class AdminDash.AdminController
The checkout method runs checks on the SQL library and login tables to see if the user is able to check out the book, and whether or not the book is available.
clearHolds(ActionEvent) - Method in class AdminDash.AdminController
method to clear all the holds students have on books, originally was going to set a daily checker to clear all holds, but creating this button leaves it up to the discretion of the Admin on when to clear all holds.
